
What Is This Project:
This modpack overhauls fundamental aspects of the game such as the enchantments, 
health system, mobs, trades, crafting and other things to make the gameplay more immersive and much more harder. 
Weak and useless features from mods included in this modpack gain a new purpose such as the armorsets. 
This modpack also has exclusive entites, enchants, and items that has not been seen anywhere else...

There are also random events in the game such as Gun Incursions, Wilted Encounters, Sculk Invasions, 
and Ghoul Huntings as well as other events at night....

Github:
This Github Repository is for updates and bugfixes, please report bugs on the Issues tab ok, thanks!
Oh BTW the mods listed in the pack are all in Curseforge and Modrinth and will be included or removeed in later versions!
